column1: IF ccr_ll_oxo_etio_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 2 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_l7b_estradiol_d is MF 0 AND ccr_sb_oh_f_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_tha_d is MF 0 AND ccr_cortisone_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1
IF ccr_etio_d is MF 0 AND ccr_zob_dhe_d is MF 2 THEN 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 1  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 1  4_Obese is 1  5_ExtremeObese is 0
